column5: KOOL today announced that it will participate in and exhibit its novel PXP System for pointofcare preparation of bone marrow concentrate BMC at The Orthobiologic Institutes TOBI 10th Annual PRP Regenerative Medicine Symposium Workshops Cadaver Labs The company is a Bronze sponsor of this years symposium being held June 68 at McCormick Place in Chicago financeyahoocomnewsther
